{
  "stem": "2133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- my-- my mother and my father spoke a good Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't speak it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just a few word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned my Yiddish in-- in a concentration camp, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, my-- three of my sisters wasn't living at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were living in Brussels, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one who was-- well, it-- it-- you know, it was very difficult for everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was very hard, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life wasn't-- was rough, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To make a living, it was rough for-- for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to constantly hear that 'you dirty Jews' anywhere you went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, and [CLEARS THROAT] when-- naturally when Hungarian took over that part of the country, and-- [CLEARS THROAT] I must have been about 13 years old-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the Hungarian 13 years old supposed to be trained for pre-army.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to call that levente, whatever that is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't know what that mean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway, you were--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At-- at 12.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At 11 to 12, they were training you for the army by-- like, after school, you have to go and march.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] you had a wooden rifle, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not-- not the a one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [CLEARS THROAT] so the Jewish-- Jewish boys wasn't doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't allow to do the Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
